# AI Assistant Rules for JuriXAI

When the user asks you to run, test, or generate an audit report for the JuriXAI Auditor:
- ALWAYS print the full content of the audit report directly in your chat response (terminal window).
- DO NOT hide the report or direct the user to a markdown artifact file (such as `jurixai_audit_report.md`) without displaying the full report content in the chat first. The user needs to see the audit results directly on their screen.
